OL,3,CGuernsey cliff path steps to reopen
OL,4,Cafter a four year closure
OL,6,FThe Clarence Battery steps in Guernsey
OL,7,Fwill be formally reopened after a four-
OL,8,Fyear closure.
OL,10,FStates of Guernsey closed the pathway
OL,11,Fin March 2020 after heavy rain caused
OL,12,Fa landslip, covering the steps.
OL,14,FAfter seven months of work
OL,15,Fcommissioned by the Committee for the
OL,16,FEnvironment & Infrastructure (E&I),
OL,17,Fthe steps once again link Guernsey's
OL,18,Feast and south coastal cliff paths.
