OL,3,CGuernsey cliff path steps to reopen
OL,4,Cafter a four year closure
OL,6,FWork mainly involved stabilising the
OL,7,Frock faces and restoring the steps to
OL,8,Fa usable condition.
OL,10,FStates of Guernsey took the
OL,11,Fopportunity to clear the edges of the
OL,12,Fstairs and level surfaces to improve
OL,13,Faccessibility.
OL,15,FAn improved drainage system is also in
OL,16,Fplace to mitigate the risk of another
OL,17,Flandslip in the future.
