OL,3,CGuernsey cliff path steps to reopen
OL,4,Cafter a four year closure
OL,6,FDespite some minor works, such as tree
OL,7,Fplanting, which is still ongoing, the
OL,8,FStates have reassured islanders that
OL,9,Fall substantial work is complete.
OL,11,FE&I President, Deputy Lindsay de
OL,12,FSausmarez, will reopen the steps at
OL,13,F1:15pm on Friday 6 September.
OL,15,FShe explained: "We really are
OL,16,Fdelighted to be able to complete this
OL,17,Fmajor project and reopen these steps,
OL,18,Fwhich I'm sure will be welcomed by
OL,19,Fislanders and visitors alike.
